<div class="title">What a Bore</div>
<div class="substance">Alprazolam (Xanax)</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Math%2B&Exact=1">Math+</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Math+. "What a Bore: An Experience with Alprazolam (Xanax) (exp31352)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Dec 1, 2007. erowid.org/exp/31352</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
